short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Turn every website into a collaborative space. Connect and interact with others while navigating through the same pages online.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
- Experience a multiplayer feel while surfing the web.
- Create private groups with your friends or coworker to create you own little world while surfing
- Engage in real-time conversations with other wanderers.

Our commitment to privacy:
- We do not save any of your data.
- We do not monitor your activities.
- We simply overlay a layer of interactive characters on top of every website.

For questions or support, join our Discord community: https://discord.gg/HM4QghGTBS
